{
  "stem": "24346.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we were really, like, stuck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But some people, however, walked on foot, and they smuggled themselves through the border and went to Russia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was a youngster.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't even think of leaving my house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And at the beginning, the Germans said, everybody must open their stores and sell their goods, just like before.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So natural, where we got our salamis and baloneys and frankfurters, the people from the firm Diamant, the firm Diamant, my father said, go pick up some stuff for our store.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went over, and I said to [INAUDIBLE]-- the lady, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Diamant, served in the store, because her husband was in the factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Diamant, I need three salamis and two of this, two of that, a nice a bundle, a package.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She gave me everything and marked in the book what I took, wrapped it up, and I walked with it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As I was walking-- and this was, by the way, Zavatska Street, where it was considered the better part of Lodz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I walked with it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had to walk through a hotel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a hotel, and the Germans occupied the hotel, no civilians there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I walked through that hotel, Hotel [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Monopol, ?] I remember was on Zavatska Street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't understand [? the deep ?] German, what they started talking to me-- an officer, because you could see it was an officer, differently dressed than the regular soldiers.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He started beating me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He took away the salamis, along with whatever I had under my arm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was down on the sidewalk, and other soldiers came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "An officer, ooh.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they started beating me with the butts of their guns.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I cried.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I screamed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But eventually they stopped, and I took off.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
